Embattled Senator, Dino Melaye has reacted to the nullification of his election by an appeal court in Abuja.Melaye said on Friday he would surely overcome as the court had ordered a rerun election.He tweeted, “I just lost my election at the Appeal Court and Fresh election ordered. In all things I give God the Praise. He who started a good thing will definitely complete it. I ask my supporters to be law-abiding as we shall always overcome. To God be the Glory.”



